cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CR 

The paper combines ideas from time-series modeling and metric learning, and uses siamese recurrent networks to learn a good similarity measure between time series. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). However, given the focus on learning a good similarity measure, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories, followed by cs.AI, cs.CL, and cs.CR.
